sprykerComponent.name: shopping-list-action-navigation
sprykerComponent.readme:
Displays a list of navigation actions which includes edit, share, print and delete links.

Code sample

{% include molecule('shopping-list-action-navigation', 'ShoppingListPage') with {
    data: {
        hasWritePermission: hasWritePermission,
        idShoppingList: shoppingList.idShoppingList,
        shoppingList: shoppingList
    }
} only %}

defines.name: data
defines.contract:
idShoppingList: required,
    hasWritePermission: required,
    shoppingList: required
